{"id":877,"date":"2017-12-22T03:07:45","date_gmt":"2017-12-22T03:07:45","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=877"},"modified":"2022-08-29T08:57:02","modified_gmt":"2022-08-29T08:57:02","slug":"mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u00e0u s\u1eafc trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">M\u00e0u s\u1eafc ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7. Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m cho nhi\u1ec1u gia ch\u1ee7 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, t\u1ea1o m\u1ea1ch c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u00e0i g\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc cho kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng:<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">T\u00f4ng m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t t\u00f4ng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t cho n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng, xanh hay kem nh\u1ea1t khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00f4ng r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u xanh l\u00e1 c\u00e2y hay v\u00e0ng chanh cho ph\u00f2ng \u0103n hay ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00ec n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch giao ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-879\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai.png 1500w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-300x216.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-768x553.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1024x737.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u s\u1eb7c s\u1ee1 gi\u00fap th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5n \u00e1t \u0111i s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng sau th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng gia ch\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 dung n\u1ea1p n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed sau gi\u1edd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-880\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"860\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1-768x516.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1-1024x688.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">M\u00e0u l\u1ea1nh. T\u00f4ng m\u00e0u n\u00e0y \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n Nam v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00ed h\u1eadu c\u00f3 m\u00f9a n\u00f3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. M\u00e0u l\u1ea1nh \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u00e1t m\u1ebb, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u00e0u xanh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 b\u1ee9c b\u1ed1i. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt s\u1ef1 n\u00f3ng b\u1ee9c cho nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f3n h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 m\u00e0u n\u00e0y th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0u n\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-881\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Mau-sac-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/up